{"tid":1276410,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知今次建制派有無唔見太陽餅","createTime":"2019-07-02T03:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T03:05:50.000Z","uid":23734,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"53fd7023e88e307cfcecb80e5d7e86a228f6066c","tid":1276410,"uid":23734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:00:39.000Z","msg":"上次台灣攻入行政院 <br />\n<strong>蕭家淇怨「太陽餅被偷吃」　網友怒合購3千片塞爆政院</strong><br />\n<br />\n//反服貿群眾23日晚間攻佔行政院，不僅打破玻璃闖進辦公室，更是極盡破壞，不少骨董家具被搬走當成擋門的工具，學生看到食物也直接打開來吃，副秘書長蕭家淇對此感到相當生氣，說學生不只偷吃他從屏東訂的蛋糕，還有太陽餅也被偷吃，甚至有人還偷了同仁放在抽屜裡的零錢。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3Fnews_id%3D338488\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Famp%2Famp_news.php%253Fnews_id%253D338488&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BkYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=bc34f03b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3Fnews_id%3D338488</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/z8YQd-ikzyk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fz8YQd-ikzyk&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BkYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=2991058f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/z8YQd-ikzyk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adeb3743c31426bac94333d2522d67d957969948","tid":1276410,"uid":120715,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14rVoKa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14rVoKa.png&h=e12af4b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82d89b302ae59e11090822b934f7ff56ade5461d","tid":1276410,"uid":50801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:05:50.000Z","msg":"有冇幾千盤汽水飲睇呢鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=